This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on abstractive summarization using transformer language models. Additionally, the paper may also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it employs neural networks for summarization. The paper may also be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with summarizing long documents, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for summarization.
